  "texts": [
    "The user can then specify the criteria for creating the lists by accessing a configuration window (Fig. 2).",
    "Here, for validation purposes, we used semantic vectors for words as extracted from DSMs, but FMG accepts any kind of vector space (e.g., encoding orthographic, phonological, visual, and other properties) for any type of items (words, sounds, images, etc.)",
    "to be used in a DRM task.",
    "For further details on this aspect, please refer to the Discussion section.",
